  "texts": [
    "Think of the words on your own (e.g., do not just look at objects in your surroundings).",
    "There were no time constraints for this task.",
    "The average human response time was 126.19 s (SD = 90.62) and the average DAT score was 76.95 (SD = 6.13).",
